Nirah's Premium Quality Strong and Durable Nylon 66 Zip ties - Loved by DIYers Premium Quality Nylon 66 Our versatile zip ties offer the flexibility to secure objects of any shape without compromising strength. Suitable for various projects, these multipurpose zip ties boast high durability and commendable ratings, and we confidently stand behind their quality. If, by any chance, you find yourself unsatisfied, feel free to reach out to us directly for prompt assistance! Multi Purpose Usage With a sharp pointed tip ensuring precise application, our zip ties boast a user-friendly locking system and a tamper-proof design for added security. They have become the trusted choice for thousands of small businesses and DIY enthusiasts, delivering reliable performance and peace of mind. Whether you're organizing cables, securing items, or tackling creative projects, our zip ties offer a versatile and dependable solution. Join the growing community of satisfied users who rely on the durability and effectiveness of our zip ties for all their fastening needs. Experience the convenience and confidence that come with using our quality products, backed by the endorsement of numerous businesses and DIYers alike. Self-Locking Fastners Our cable ties feature automatic self-locking due to teeth-like grooves on one side. This unique mechanism proves highly practical for bundling various items together effortlessly, whether at home, in the office, garden, or workshop. Utilizing these ties is a breeze – simply insert the tail through the ratchet hole in the head, tighten, and trim the excess with scissors or a cable tie gun. Their user-friendly design ensures easy and efficient use in various settings. Heat and Cold Resistant Nirah's zip ties are engineered to withstand extreme temperatures, showcasing exceptional heat and cold resistance for reliable performance in diverse environments. Whether you're working in scorching heat or freezing cold, Nirah's zip ties remain resilient, ensuring a secure and enduring fastening solution. The heat resistance ensures stability and strength in high-temperature settings, making them suitable for applications where other ties might falter. Similarly, the cold resistance ensures flexibility and functionality in freezing temperatures, offering peace of mind in various outdoor and industrial scenarios.

Nylon Non-Releasable Cable Ties, constructed from high-quality Nylon 6.6 (Polyamide 6.6), are a vital fastening solution with a myriad of applications. This thread explores the features, benefits, and reasons why these cable ties should be a staple in every toolkit. Material Specifications: Crafted from Nylon 6.6, these cable ties boast exceptional durability and strength. The choice of material ensures longevity and resilience in various environmental conditions. With a Flammability Rating of UL94V-2 and a Flame-Retardant nature, they provide an added layer of safety, making them suitable for applications where fire resistance is crucial. Operating Temperature Range: The operational flexibility of these cable ties is noteworthy, with an impressive Operating Temperature Range from -13°F to 194°F. This wide range makes them adaptable to diverse settings, ensuring reliability in both extreme cold and heat. Common Uses: Primarily designed as fasteners, Nylon Non-Releasable Cable Ties find widespread use in bundling and securing items, especially electrical cables and wires. Their self-extinguishing property (UL94V-2) adds an extra layer of safety, making them an ideal choice for applications where fire safety is a priority. Features and Benefits: High Quality: The use of UL approved nylon 6.6 ensures a high-quality product that meets industry standards.Versatility: Suitable for a multitude of uses, these cable ties provide a secure fastening solution for various applications.Ease of Use: Designed for easy threading, they simplify the process of bundling and securing items, making them user-friendly.Self-Extinguishing: The self-extinguishing property to UL94V-2 adds a crucial safety feature, particularly in environments where fire resistance is essential. In conclusion, Nirah's Premium Nylon Non-Releasable Cable Ties are more than just fasteners; they are a reliable and versatile solution that enhances safety and organization across various industries. Investing in these cable ties ensures a dependable and secure fastening solution for a wide array of applications.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Number of Each Included in Assortment of 1000. Width of Longer Ties
reviews.reviewText: 1. I couldn't find in the description how many of each size are included in the assortment of 1000.I received my shipment today and there are 200 of each size.Some sellers include a greater number of less costly small sizes with assortments.2. I selected this vendor because they provided more specifications than others. Mainly, I was interested in the shortest length being thin so they wouldn't be very visible. I was restringing a set of white wire Christmas lights on a white outdoor decorationThis seller provided the width of each length zip tie while the "Amazon's Choice" seller did not specifically mention the width of each different length. Their only width listed appeared that all their 1000 assortment had the same width which matched the width of the longest tie. If accurate, that would make the smallest tie more visible than I preferred.3. One thing that surprised me was the width of the larger lengths which was narrower than what I expected. (Since I was mainly interested in the shortest length, I did not compare the widths of the longer lengths between sellers). After arrival, I compared to "Amazon's Choice" and the widths were the same.I also compared to a black assortment I purchased 5 years ago from Amazon. That manufacturer is no longer listed on Amazon or a Google search. While the longer ties are only 3 mm wide with this purchase, ties I ordered 5 years ago are 4.8 mm wide. This wider width seems more appropriate for the strength probably needed when using long ties.
Good for many things. Durable and easy to use.
